Pets/Pets buffs and spells<br>
Nukes/Utils (See invis, Gate, Cancel Magic, mics spells)<br>
Foci summons/All other summons ordered (weapons, armor, items)<br>
(skip lots of pages until 30+)<br>
Obsolete spells/obsolete spells <p><center><a href="http://www.legion-whiterose.com"><img src="http://www.legion-whiterose.com/signatures/legionnaires/loralon.jpg"></a><br><i><b>Verba Volant, Scripta Manent</b></i></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzacatac.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zacatac</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1114<br> <font color=#333333>(8/26/02 7:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1494.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Book Setup</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I would never (or very rarely) use that lv1 Nuke<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> I use it all the time to pull with actually when farming green stuff <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
